<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Kinzix</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-04 23:53:22</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>you need a fire goblin skin from Sol A.<BR>
a frost goblin skin from permafrost.<BR>
a scroll of Elemental armor (about 80plat from mage guild).<BR>
and a twice woven cloak from fearie guards.<BR>
only the cloak is NO DROP, but the others can be bought or looted.<BR>
if you are low its best to sit at the zone and have the higher level people clear out the mobs you need and loot them.<BR>
Good luck and be careful of the trains and lava in Sol A.</font></td></tr></table>
